nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The Partner Central homepage presents a collection of headline sections that highlight the latest partner‑focused news, product announcements, and program updates, such as joint messaging with Cisco, Pure Storage, and Nutanix, marketing insights, new product availability, and the upcoming FY26 Elevate Partner Program. Its primary purpose is to give distributors a quick, centralized view of current initiatives and resources that drive the hybrid‑cloud and partner ecosystem. The page is organized into distinct banner‑style blocks for each announcement, providing easy navigation to deeper content without any tables or forms.

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The Sales page in Partner Central presents an overview of Nutanix’s enablement and sales resources, organized under headings such as Content Library, Sales Resources, and Test‑Drive Partner Center. Its primary purpose is to give distributors quick access to tools, documentation, and guidance that support the sales process and help move opportunities through Nutanix’s defined sales stages. Key visible sections include a brief description of the resource hub, a call‑to‑action for growing and closing business, and an explanation of the sales‑stage framework used for forecasting.

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The Renewals page in Partner Central presents a high‑level overview of enablement and sales resources that partners can use to drive Nutanix business growth. Its primary function is to give distributors quick access to tools, documentation, and guidance—organized around the defined Nutanix sales stages and forecasting categories—to help them manage and close renewal opportunities more efficiently. Key visible sections include a header with navigation links (Content Library, Renewals Resources, View As) and a central content block describing the purpose of the resources and the sales‑stage framework.
headers: Renewal Insights Partner Admin User Guide

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The Programs page in Partner Central presents an overview of Nutanix’s Elevate Partner and Elevate Distributor programs, highlighting the available enablement and sales resources. Its primary purpose is to inform distributors about the program’s requirements, benefits, and rewards, and to guide them toward maximizing those advantages. The page is organized into key sections that introduce the resource library, outline how to leverage the program, and provide links to detailed information on eligibility, benefits, and supporting materials.

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The Learn page within Partner Central presents a centralized hub of enablement and sales resources for Nutanix partners, featuring sections that highlight training programs, certification pathways, and up‑to‑date product information. Its primary purpose is to give partners quick access to educational content and tools that help them master Nutanix’s cloud‑infrastructure and hyper‑converged solutions. Key visible elements include a header navigation bar (Content Library, Learn, Partner Central, View As) and concise messaging that promotes the availability of training, certifications, and the latest Nutanix updates.
headers: Nutanix Certified Sales Representative (NCSR): Nutanix Basics

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The **Partner Central – Marketing** page presents an overview of Nutanix’s enablement and sales resources that partners can use to drive demand. Its primary function is to give partners quick access to ready‑to‑use marketing assets, co‑branded programs, and personalized Test Drive Partner Center (TDPC) links that prospects can use to experience Nutanix solutions. Key visible sections include a content library banner, a “Supercharge Your Marketing” call‑to‑action, and a description of how partners can share collateral and TDPC links to nurture customers.
